{"tid":2228856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"放生拆連儂牆藍絲 港大保安員停職","createTime":"2020-10-04T02:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T06:53:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"63a30034722feae7d89966ee28914a708215c240","tid":2228856,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/RYX3PE5ZKFBCZO2X6CCITUAFKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FRYX3PE5ZKFBCZO2X6CCITUAFKY%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdtC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=a0e24622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FRYX3PE5ZKFBCZO2X6CCITUAFKY%2F&h=9997b0ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/RYX3PE5ZKFBCZO2X6CCITUAFKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n放生拆連儂牆藍絲 港大保安員停職<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】十多名操鄉音的藍絲上月底闖入港大校園，撕毀連儂牆，又到學生會大樓撕走玻璃門上的文宣，其間在場有多名港大保安，但任由他們離去，沒有阻止。港大校委會本科生代表李梓成在facebook發帖透露，與校方管理層溝通後，校方向涉事保安發出警告信，並需要停職兩周，其間需接受訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人向破壞者道謝舉拇指<br />\n<br />\n李梓成指，港大連儂牆被毀事件中，保安處於被動，當中兩名人員更分別因向破壞者舉拇指及說出「Thank you」，引起巨大爭議。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李梓成續稱，期望日後發生類似事件時，校方能吸取教訓，「畢竟調停衝突、秉公制止校園內的事件，對保安而言應該是很基本的要求」。他已透過大學有關人員傳話，表示港大同學從來以事論事，並不盲目仇恨，更不願在這艱難時期使人丟飯碗，而是目睹不合理的事，當然義憤填膺，希望有關保安完成訓練後，他日能更好地處理類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n上月27日晚上約7時，30多名藍絲從港鐵站走到大學街，撕毀四幅連儂牆，又推倒學生會旗幟，其間有同行人士拍片，聲稱「唔希望自己嘅仔女喺咁唔乾淨嘅大學入面讀書」而出手，隨後又闖入學生會大樓撕走玻璃門上的文宣。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J2rkvCk71ECxtwaVwM3kFvk8Fj8=/699x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XLYJDE4ZWVF2HEPKMKUH6QKAQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ2rkvCk71ECxtwaVwM3kFvk8Fj8%3D%2F699x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXLYJDE4ZWVF2HEPKMKUH6QKAQ4.jpg&h=d1066935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多名藍絲上月27日到港大拆連儂牆，保安僅勸喻他們離開。"},{"pid":"c82838f5b70780d52fd8efe933696a11633004c4","tid":2228856,"uid":52791,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"停職? 炒撚晒佢啦"},{"pid":"5202f41dd4fca67297b5b271c6f2d289d6619daa","tid":2228856,"uid":25673,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c82838f5b70780d52fd8efe933696a11633004c4","tid":2228856,"uid":52791,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"停職? 炒撚晒佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"肯停算好㗎啦，正常係己訓斥就算"},{"pid":"6b7c369ff8c4040d7f817e07e5b5b491594ba6c2","tid":2228856,"uid":58851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"根本係監守自盜, 保安同犯法者蛇鼠一窩<br />\n<br />\n蛇: 保安<br />\n鼠: 藍絲"},{"pid":"61c43162298065993918987bffdf412605da323a","tid":2228856,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"認住個樣<br />\n以後做少一樣都投訴<br />\n捉唔到刑事毁壞藍屍<br />\n咁就等班lala 隊還"},{"pid":"52548f2333a0a8fb53ff0eede8eab64630e73317","tid":2228856,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"淨係停職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5071614225072eb190391da13062a8d77cc06ae6","tid":2228856,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"希望班港大生以後每次行過見到佢都屌佢幾句"},{"pid":"3823eb5e0a402f585cec23f115c86ff89dbef54f","tid":2228856,"uid":297416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5202f41dd4fca67297b5b271c6f2d289d6619daa","tid":2228856,"uid":25673,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c82838f5b70780d52fd8efe933696a11633004c4","tid":2228856,"uid":52791,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"停職? 炒撚晒佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"肯停算好㗎啦，正常係己訓斥就算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:54:00.000Z